{{Pagenav|数据驱动|数据驱动/物品|snakecase=1}}{{lowercase c|minecraft:block_placer|minecraft:block_placer}}{{infobox component
| domain = item
| type = component
| api = dd
| format-version = 1.20.10
| added = 1.16.100.56
}}{{featured article}}
'''{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}'''用于设置物品放置方块的功能。

==模式==
<syntaxhighlight lang="text"">
object "minecraft:block_placer" : opt
{
    string "block"
    array "use_on"<0-*> : opt
    {
        "<any array element>" : opt
    }
}
</syntaxhighlight>

==结构 ==
<div class="treeview">
* {{json|obj|minecraft:block_placer}}：根对象。
**{{json|str|block|required=1}}：定义所放置方块的[[赋命名空间标识符]]。
**{{json|arr|use_on}}：定义可放置在哪些方块上，空值表示可放置在任何方块上。
**{{json|bool|replace_block_item}}：设置为<code>true</code>时，该物品将被注册为是该方块对应的物品。当该方块被破坏或拾起后将默认返回该物品。
</div>

==示例 ==
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"minecraft:block_placer": {
  "block": "iron_block",
  "use_on": [
    "dirt",
    "grass"
  ],
  "replace_block_item": true
}
</syntaxhighlight>

==历史==
{{History|Bedrock}}
{{History||1.16.100|snap=1.16.100.56|加入了{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}。}}
{{History||1.20.10|snap=1.20.10.21|将{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}移出实验性玩法。}}
{{History||1.21.40|snap=1.21.40.22|在{{experiment|ucft}}中，为使用{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}物品组件的自定义物品加入了使用所引用的<code>block</code>作为物品图标的支持。}}
{{History||1.21.40|snap=1.21.40.23|为{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}物品组件加入了<code>replace_block_item</code>字段。}}
{{History||1.21.60|snap=1.21.60.25|将{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}的<code>replace_block_item</code>字段移出实验性玩法。}}
{{History|foot}}

==参考==
有关{{samp|minecraft:block_placer}}组件的用法，可以查阅[https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/minecraft/creator/reference/content/itemreference/examples/itemcomponents/minecraft_block_placer?view=minecraft-bedrock-stable 微软文档]。

