{{lowercase c|minecraft:aggregate_feature|minecraft:aggregate_feature}}{{infobox schema
| title = minecraft:aggregate_feature
| image = aggregate_feature.png
| domain = features
| type = 聚合地物
| format-version = 
| added = ?
}}
'''聚合地物（Aggregate Feature）'''用于以任意顺序在同一输入位置放置一组地物。
==语法==
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"minecraft:aggregate_feature": {
  "description": {
    "identifier": "<par1>"
  },
  "early_out": "<par2>",
  "features": <par3>
}
</syntaxhighlight>
==结构==
<div class="treeview">
*{{json|obj|minecraft:aggregate_feature}}：根对象。
**{{json|obj|description|required=1}}：描述。
***{{json|identifier|identifier|required=1}}：设置此地物的[[赋命名空间标识符]]，其标识符必须与文件名匹配。
**{{json|enum|early_out}}：设置放置地物的[[Manual:minecraft:aggregate_feature#放置规则|规则]]。默认值为{{cd|none}}。
**{{json|arr|features|required=1}}：设置要放置的目标地物，填写其赋命名空间标识符。
</div>
==放置规则==
默认情况下，聚合地物会尝试放置地物列表里面的每个地物。通过{{cd|early_out}}属性可以设置聚合地物尝试放置目标地物的规则，它接受以下三个值：
{| class="wikitable"
!值
!注释
|-
|{{cd|none}}
|尝试放置每个目标地物。
|-
|{{cd|first_failure}}
|在首次放置失败后停止放置目标地物。
|-
|{{cd|first_success}}
|在首次放置成功后停止放置目标地物。
|}
==示例==
下面的示例将在遗迹周围散布多种不同的植物。
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
{
  "format_version": "1.3.0",
  "minecraft:aggregate_feature": {
    "description": {
      "identifier": "example:monument_with_flowers_feature"
    },
    "features": [
      "monument_feature",
      "scatter_white_flowers_feature",
      "scatter_yellow_flower_feature"
    ]
  }
}
</syntaxhighlight>
==历史==
{{History|bedrock}}
{{History||?|snap=?|加入了{{samp|minecraft:aggregate_feature}}。}}
{{History|foot}}
==漏洞==
{{issue list|minecraft:aggregate_feature}}

{{navbox schema}}

