| title = minecraft:tree_feature
| image = tree_feature.png
| domain = features
| type = 树地物
| format-version = 
| added = ?
}}
'''树地物（Tree Feature）'''用于构造并生成一棵树。

树地物的属性结构大致分为四部分：基本属性、树干属性、树冠属性和根部属性，它们又由许多子属性组成。

==语法==
===基本属性===
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"minecraft:tree_feature": {
  "description": {
    "identifier": "<par1>"
  },
  "base_block": <par2>,
  "base_cluster": {
    "may_replace": <par3>,
    "num_clusters": <par4>,
    "cluster_radius": <par5>
  },
  "may_grow_on": <par6>,
  "may_replace": <par7>,
  "may_grow_through": <par8>
  //树干属性
  //树冠属性
  //根部属性
}
</syntaxhighlight>
===树干属性===
<tabbertransclude>
Manual:Minecraft:tree_feature/常规树干语法|常规树干
