Manual:Minecraft:tree_feature/花俏的树干语法|花俏的树干
Manual:Minecraft:tree_feature/红树树干语法|红树树干
Manual:Minecraft:tree_feature/巨型树干语法|巨型树干
</tabbertransclude>
===树冠属性===
