Manual:Minecraft:tree_feature/随机传播树冠语法|随机传播树冠
</tabbertransclude>
===根部属性===
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"mangrove_roots": {
  "max_root_width": <par1>,
  "max_root_length": <par2>,
  "root_block": <par3>,
  "above_root": {
    "above_root_chance": <par4>,
    "above_root_block": <par5>
  }，
  "muddy_root_block": <par6>,
  "mud_block": <par7>,
  "y_offset": <par8>,
  "roots_may_grow_through": <par9>,
  "root_decoration": {
    "decoration_chance": <par10>,
    "decoration_block": <par11>,
    "num_steps": <par12>,
    "step_direction": "<par13>"
  }
}
</syntaxhighlight>

==结构==
<div class="treeview">
*{{json|obj|minecraft:tree_feature}}：根对象。
**{{json|obj|description|required=1}}：描述。
***{{json|id|identifier|required=1}}：设置此地物的[[赋命名空间标识符]]，其标识符必须与文件名匹配。
**{{json|str;arr|base_block}}
**{{json|obj|base_cluster}}
***{{json|arr|may_replace}}
***{{json|int|num_clusters|required=1}}：最小值为1。
***{{json|int|cluster_radius|required=1}}：最小值为0。
**{{json|arr|may_grow_on}}
**{{json|arr|may_replace}}
**{{json|arr|may_grow_through}}
**{{nbt inherit/feature/trunk}}
