{{lowercase c|minecraft:recipe_furnace|minecraft:recipe_furnace}}{{infobox schema
| title = minecraft:recipe_furnace
| imagearea =<div>{{Furnace
|Input= Raw Beef,1
|Output= Cooked Beef,1
|Fuel= Coal,1
}}</div>
| domain = recipes
| type = 熔炉配方
| format-version = 
| added = ?
}}
{{redirect|烧炼配方|熔炉配方的其他信息|mcwzh:烧炼#配方{{!}}Minecraft Wiki:烧炼#配方}}{{about|熔炉配方|一种在Minecraft里提炼或加热物品的方式|mcwzh:烧炼{{!}}Minecraft Wiki:烧炼|烧炼的技术信息|烧炼}}
'''熔炉配方（Furnace Recipe）'''可将输入[[物品]]转化为输出物品。

==语法==
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"minecraft:recipe_furnace": {
  "description": {
    "identifier": "<par1>"
  },
  "tags": <par2>,
  "input": <par3>,
  "output": <par4>
}
</syntaxhighlight>
==结构==
<div class="treeview">
*{{json|obj|minecraft:recipe_furnace}}：根对象。
**{{json|obj|description|required=1}}：描述。
***{{json|identifier|identifier|required=1}}：设置此配方的[[赋命名空间标识符]]。
**{{json|arr|tags|required=1}}：设置该配方的[[配方#标签|标签]]。
**{{json|item reference;obj|input|required=1}}：设置输入物品的赋命名空间标识符。
***{{nbt inherit/schema/item_reference}}
**{{json|item reference;obj|output|required=1}}：设置输出物品的赋命名空间标识符。
***{{nbt inherit/schema/item_reference}}
</div>
==示例==
下面的示例所构建的配方将把[[生牛肉]]转化为[[牛排]]。
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
{
  "format_version": "1.12",
  "minecraft:recipe_furnace": {
    "description": {
    "identifier": "minecraft:furnace_beef"
    },
    "tags": ["furnace", "smoker", "campfire", "soul_campfire"],
    "input": "minecraft:beef",
    "output": "minecraft:cooked_beef"
  }
}
</syntaxhighlight>

