{{lowercase c|minecraft:beards_and_shavers|minecraft:beards_and_shavers}}{{infobox schema
| title = minecraft:beards_and_shavers
| image = beards_and_shavers.png
| domain = features
| type = 胡须与剃刀
| format-version = 
| added = ?
}}
'''胡须与剃刀（Beards and Shavers）'''用于为地物的生成同时提供平台与空间。

“胡须”指平台，“剃刀”指空间。胡须与剃刀生成的平台近似一个半球体，截面平整。
==语法==
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
"minecraft:beards_and_shavers": {
  "description": {
    "identifier": "<par1>"
  },
  "places_feature": "<par2>",
  "bounding_box_min": <par3>,
  "bounding_box_max": <par4>,
  "y_delta": <par5>,
  "surface_block_type": <par6>,
  "subsurface_block_type": <par7>,
  "beard_raggedness_min": <par8>,
  "beard_raggedness_max": <par9>
}
</syntaxhighlight>
==结构==
<div class="treeview">
*{{json|obj|minecraft:beards_and_shavers}}：根对象。
**{{json|obj|description|required=1}}：描述。
***{{json|identifier|identifier|required=1}}：设置此地物的[[赋命名空间标识符]]，其标识符必须与文件名匹配。
**{{json|feature reference|places_feature|required=1}}：设置要放置在平台上的地物，填写其符命名空间标识符。
**{{json|arr|bounding_box_min|required=1}}
**{{json|arr|bounding_box_max|required=1}}
**{{json|float|y_delta|required=1}}
**{{json|block reference;obj|surface_block_type|required=1}}：设置平台表面的方块类型。
***{{nbt inherit/schema/block reference}}
**{{json|block reference;obj|subsurface_block_type|required=1}}：设置平台表面以下的方块类型。
***{{nbt inherit/schema/block reference}}
**{{json|float|beard_raggedness_min}}
**{{json|float|beard_raggedness_max}}
</div>
==示例 ==
下面的示例将为[[结构]]提供平台。
<syntaxhighlight lang="json" line>
{
  "format_version": "1.13.0"
  "minecraft:beards_and_shavers": {
    "description": {
      "identifier": "example:provide_a_platform_for_the_structure"
    },
    "places_feature": "minecraft:feature_that_places_a_structure",
    "bounding_box_min": [ -2, 0, -2 ],
    "bounding_box_max": [ 2, 8, 2 ],
    "y_delta": 2.0,
    "surface_block_type": "minecraft:grass",
    "subsurface_block_type": "minecraft:dirt",
    "beard_raggedness_min": 0.1,
    "beard_raggedness_max": 0.3
  }
}
</syntaxhighlight>
